name: Amateur-Only Street Fighter V Tournament
details: Are you new to Street Fighter V? Wanna test your skills and combos against other players of a similar skill level? Wanna win $25,000? Enter into this amateur Street Fighter tournament and RISE UP!

name: $1,000,000 Guilty Gear Strive Tournament
details: Do YOU know the smell of the game? Enter this tournament for Guilty Gear Strive to test your metal and ROCK OUT!

name: $100 Super Smash Bros. Melee Tournament
details: Y'all already know what it is! The original Nintendo All-Stars Battle Royale is here! Test your skills against some of the best Melee players in the world for a piece of this $100 prize pool!

name: The Themes of Robotics and Futurism in MegaMan
details: There's more than what meets the eye in this popular action platforming series. Explore the themes and ethics of robotics and futurism in this 5-hour long presentation.

name: The State of Video Game Preservation Today
details: Some of your favorite games may be disappearing sooner than you think. Join the 2 hour-long discussion on the state of video game preservation today and what can be done to save them.

name: How to Get Better at Fighting Games
details: Want to learn the basics that will get you good at any fighting game? Join this informative discussion to learn everything from spacing to execution!
